  "description": "If you fail a saving throw, you can reroll it with a bonus equal to your Fighter level (currently, [[lookup @classes.fighter.levels]]). You must use the new roll, and you can't use this feature again until you finish a Long Rest.\n\nYou can use this feature twice before a Long Rest starting at level 13 and three times before a Long Rest starting at level 17.\n\nFoundry Note\n\nThis feature's maximum usages scale automatically as you level up.",
